ufw 

Checking the status:
sudo ufw status (gives the status of the firewall)

Setting up:
	Incoming traffic:
		sudo ufw default deny incoming

	Outgoing traffic:
		sudo ufw default allow outgoing

	Allowing SSH:
		sudo ufw allow 2222/tcp (2222 is being set up since Vagrant used 2222 as the default ssh port)

	Allowing HTTP:
		sudo ufw allow www

Enabling the Firewall
	sudo ufw enable